{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_08_01",
  "title": "miho 1話 免許証です",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……やっと事務所に戻って来られた\n後はメールを返して、それと……あれ、mihoさん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… finally back at the office.\nJust need to reply to emails‚ and… oh‚ miho?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8299476357,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2903.3856976,
          "startTime": 7.7333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3670.0523642,
          "startTime": 8.4999999999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。今掃除中で邪魔なので\nさっさとどいていただけると助かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. I'm cleaning right now‚ so you're in the way.\nIt would be helpful if you could move aside quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "し、失礼しました……あれ、mihoさんが\n事務所の掃除をしてくれてたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-My apologies… Wait‚ miho‚\nhave you been cleaning the office?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "いつも沙季が整頓してくれているようですが\n子供にばかりやらせるのも大人として情けないですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Usually Saki seems to keep things tidy‚\nbut letting a child do it all feels pathetic as an adult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "いくら片付けても、いつの間にかまた散らかって……\n今日なんて、雑誌が読み散らかされていましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how much I clean‚ it's messy again in no time…\nEven today‚ magazines were left scattered after being read.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……その雑誌、俺が読んでたやつです……\n以後整理整頓を徹底いたします、はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry… those magazines are the ones I was reading…\nI'll make sure to keep things organized from now on‚ yes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル達の模範となるべきマネージャーが\n率先して堕落していてどうするんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A manager‚ who should be a role model for idols‚\nshouldn't be the one leading the way in laziness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "それにアイドル誌に混じって車の雑誌もありましたけど\n業務中に何をやっていたんですか、まったく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ there was a car magazine mixed with the idol ones.\nWhat exactly were you doing during work hours‚ honestly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ。たしかに車の雑誌なんですけど、特集記事に\nアイドルへのインタビューがあったもので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ it's not like that. It is a car magazine‚ but\nthere was an interview with an idol in the feature…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、アイドルが愛車を語るとかそういう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ those \"idols talking about their cars\" pieces…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "納得しました。貴方、免許は持っているようですけど\n運転しているところは、あまり見たことありませんし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. You seem to have a license‚\nbut I haven't really seen you behind the wheel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ基本的には、電車かタクシーですしね……\nそういえば、mihoさんは免許持ってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ usually I take the train or a taxi…\nCome to think of it‚ do you have a license‚ miho?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "一応、昔に取りましたよ\n……なんでそこで、意外そうな顔をするんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I took it a long time ago‚ for the most part.\n…Why that look of surprise?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "免許証です、どうぞ心ゆくまでご覧になって下さい\nああ、悪用はしないで下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here's my license‚ feel free to look as much as you'd like.\nOh‚ but please don't misuse it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 95.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いや別に疑ってる訳じゃなくてですね……あ、凄い\nマニュアル車で取ってる。運転お好きなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I wasn't doubting you… oh‚ wow.\nYou got a manual license. Do you like driving?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、どうせ取るなら、マニュアルとオートマと\n両方運転出来た方が便利かと思っただけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I just thought it would be more convenient to be able\nto drive both manual and automatic cars.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "……昔、仕事がだんだん増えてきた頃に\n葉ちゃんと、車がほしいという話になったんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…A long time ago‚ back when our workload started increasing‚\nHa-chan and I talked about wanting a car.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "移動のたびに、他人の目を気にしなければならないのは\n結構なストレスですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having to worry about the public eye every time we travel\nwas quite a lot of stress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうですね\n特に、人気急上昇中のアイドルともなると",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That makes sense.\nEspecially for idols whose popularity is skyrocketing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "それで、二人とも免許を取れたら\nドライブで温泉にでも泊まりに行こう、と約束して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we agreed that once we both got our licenses‚\nwe'd drive to a hot spring and stay over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……免許はお互いどうにか取れたものの\n忙しくて、日帰りでしか行けなかったんですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… we both managed to get our licenses‚\nbut we were so busy we could only go for day trips.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "それにあの時は結局、「疲れたでしょ」と\n葉ちゃんがほとんど運転をかわってくれましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And back then‚ in the end‚ Ha-chan took over\nmost of the driving‚ saying \"You must be tired.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……まぁ、昔の話ですよ\nいらぬ雑談をしてしまいましたね、忘れて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… well‚ that's an old story.\nI've prattled on with useless chatter. Please forget it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……俺も昔、免許を取れ取れと\n言われたことを、思い出しましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… it just reminded me of when I was\ntold to get a license a long time ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 178.9500010173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "海外の自動車メーカーが日本に進出するにあたって\nCMと宣伝用のキービジュアルを作りたい、ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An overseas car manufacturer is entering the Japanese market\nand wants to create a CM and key visuals for promotion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.2333343506,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 179.8333343506
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "CM撮影では、出来れば演者当人が実際にスポーツカー\nを運転するところを撮りたい……と。なるほど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the CM‚ they want the actor themselves to actually\ndrive the sports car if possible… I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.3666676839,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 233.33333330000983,
          "startTime": 189.0333343506
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "私に声を掛けた理由はそれですか\n確かにスポーツカーはマニュアル車が多いですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why you approached me.\nIt's true that sports cars are often manual‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.2000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk020.m4a",
      "text": "この事務所、そもそも十八歳以下の子が多くて\n運転出来る人間が少ないですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and this agency has many girls under eighteen‚\nso there aren't many people who can drive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.3000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですが、でもそれ以上に、mihoさんなら\n高級車のラグジュアリーな雰囲気に合いますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true‚ but more than that‚ if it's you‚ miho‚\nyou fit the luxury atmosphere of high-end cars.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.1666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "この間のお話だと運転もお上手そうなので、イメージに\nぴったりかなと。嫌でなければ、先方に提案してみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Based on our talk‚ you seemed skilled at driving too‚\nso I thought you'd be a perfect fit. If you're okay with it‚ I'll propose it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.3666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk021.m4a",
      "text": "運転が……上手……\n取って付けたように持ち上げて下さらなくても結構です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Skilled at… driving…\nThere's no need to flatter me like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.1333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk022.m4a",
      "text": "ともあれ、仕事はお引き受けします\n高級車のCMなら、実績としても申し分ありませんしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At any rate‚ I'll take the job.\nA luxury car CM would be an excellent addition to my career.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.4666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。一応ですが、運転の方も大丈夫ですか？\nスポーツカーなので、普通車とは勝手が違いますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. Just to be sure‚ the driving part is okay too?\nIt's a sports car‚ so it'll feel different from a regular one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.0797448121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk023.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、そちらもやりますよ\nそれだけ断るなんて、先方にも失礼ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I'll do that too.\nRefusing only that part would be rude to the client.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.3333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いざとなればCG合成でもCMは作れるので\n断っていただいても、別に問題はありませんが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can create a CM with CG if necessary‚\nso it wouldn't be a problem if you declined…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.5000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk024.m4a",
      "text": "だから、やると言っているでしょう\nそのために私に声を掛けたんじゃないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you‚ I'll do it.\nIsn't that why you called me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.5000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk025.m4a",
      "text": "最近は、車雑誌にもアイドルの記事が載りますし\n運転好きとアピールするに越したことはありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These days‚ idol articles even appear in car magazines‚\nand it doesn't hurt to appeal as someone who likes driving.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.0666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。では運転シーンも\n撮影可能と先方には返事しておきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. I'll let the client know\nthat the driving scenes are good to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.6333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（なんか少しムキになってたような……）\n（実はmihoさん、案外運転が好きなのかもしれないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She seemed a bit competitive just now…）\n（Maybe miho actually likes driving more than she lets on.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 293.7000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}